    FIMTDD

    public static class FIMTDD.FIMTDDSplitNode
extends HoeffdingTree.SplitNode
implements FIMTDD.AdaptationCompatibleNode
    A modified SplitNode method implementing the extra information regarding it's parent, and the ability to track the error rate and perform Page-Hinckley tests
